[Result ""]
{SOUTH has no way to tell whether NORTH can provide one winner or not.

So she takes the bold approach and bids 4

♥

.

If the opening lead is a ♠ or a

♦

then SOUTH

will probably make the game. Otherwise she will likely go down one.}
